Description: This package is the umbrella package for 4 other packages that contain
the functions for constructing a machine learning predictive ecosystem maps.
1)PEMprepr for import and preparation of model inputs; 
2)PEMsamplr for building sample plans and preparing collected field data; 
3)PEMmodelr for building and evaluating a machine-learned model;
4)PEMmapr for creating final raster and vector maps from the ML model
